### Update or add a reaction for this Immunization - reaction.date & reaction.manifestation
PUT http://localhost:8080/fhir/Immunization/{id}
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Immunization",
  "id": "{id}",
  "reaction": [
    {
      "date": "YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss+TZ",
      "detail": {
        "reference": "Observation/{observation-id}"
      },
      "reported": true
    }
  ]
}

